profile: As one of the largest and most solidly established storage facilities in the Airdrie area. Safeway Mini Storage has the experience to deliver quality services with pride. Safeway Mini Storage located in Airdrie, AB is a secure, fully fenced self storage property with 24 hour on site video surveillance. Safeway Mini Storage offers 7 different unit sizes at low and affordable rates. All units have 10" ceilings. No set up fees, security deposits or hidden cost and available on a month to month basis. We accept all major credit cards, debit cards, money orders, cheques, cash and pre-authorized payments. Drive up to your unit with convenient and easy access 7 days a week. Our units are clean and well maintained by our local on site staff who will service you with excellent customer service.
